Hello all active devs.
This channel will be used to describe and discuss the Release Plan for OpenCPN Version 5.12.x.
This is the "official" plan, and all modifications and notifications will be made here.

Basic Plan Outline.

Feature Freeze: 15 April, 2025

Beta Test starts: 1 May, 2025

Target Release Date: 15 June, 2025
